                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": "LIKE",
                  "marks": [
                    {
                      "type": "code"
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " clause can result in inefficient query execution plans, potentially causing performance bottlenecks."
